Warbixintan ayaa yareysay xaaladaha degdegga ah ee dadweynaha, gaar ahaan marka dalka oo dhan uu isu diyaarinayo xafladda gu'ga, waana waqti muhiim ah oo laga maqnaa xakamaynta cudurka, markii uu weli ahaa mid aad u hooseeya magaalada Wuhan.
Hay'adaha xakamaynta cudurrada ee Shiinaha ayaa laga yaabaa inay qaataan casharradan adag oo ay si adag u hagaajin doonaan mustaqbalka.
Tusaale ahaan, hay'adahaas waa inay (1) aad uga taxaddaraan marka ay sameeyaan ogeysiisyo dadweyne, maxaa yeelay erayada oo dhami aad ayey muhiim ugu yihiin muwaadiniinta waxayna u beddeli karaan dabeecadahooda iyo go'aankooda; (2) aad uga taxaddaraan oo uga jawaabaan wararka aan sax ahayn ee ka yimaada rugta caafimaadka halkii ay ka sugeyso warbixin rasmi ah dhakhaatiirta ama saraakiisha; (3) aad uga adag yihiin inay ka hortagaan cudurrada faafa ee laga yaabo inay dhacaan marxaladda hore halkii ay isku dayi lahaayeen inay ku dhacaan dadka kale; iyo (4) si ka badan inta hore ee lagu dhaqmo tijaabooyin bartilmaameedsan oo wax ku ool ah si kor loogu qaado wacyiga dadweynaha ee cudurka iyo in la sameeyo tijaabooyin iyo jawaab-celin bulsho oo joogto ah.
Cudurka COVID-19 ee uu sababay fayraska SARS-CoV-2 wuxuu bilaabmay dabayaaqadii Diseembar 2019.
