Si kastaba ha noqotee, waxaa jira kala duwanaansho la taaban karo oo u dhexeeya COVID-19 iyo SARS, kuwaas oo lagama maarmaan u ah ka hortagga faafitaanka iyo daaweynta bukaanka.
COVID-19 waxay saameyneysaa dadka da'da ah in ka badan dadka da'da yar, ragga in ka badan dumarka, iyo halista iyo dhimashada bukaannada da'da weyn ayaa ka sarreysa kuwa da'da yar.
SARS ayaa ka badan COVID-19 (10.91% iyo 1.44%).
Bukaanka qaba COVID-19 waxay u gudbiyaan fayraska dadka kale xitaa haddii aysan lahayn calaamado, halka bukaanka qaba SARS aysan lahayn wax calaamado ah marka ay qabaan xaalad xanuun daran, taas oo ka dhigaysa inay ka adagtahay in la xakameeyo faafitaanka COVID-19 marka loo eego SARS.
Tani waxay si gaar ah u sharaxdaa sababta SARS-CoV-2 ay uga sii dhaqso badan tahay SARS-CoV.
