Bishii Diseembar 2019, coronavirus cusub ee 2019 (2019-nCoV) ayaa sababay dillaac, oo hadda si rasmi ah loogu magac daray cudurka coronavirus ee 2019 (COVID-19), waxaana loo magacaabay cudurka neef-mareenka ee daran ee loo yaqaan 'SARS-CoV-2'.
