Laakiin shaqadooda waxay sidoo kale u baahan tahay cusbooneysiin iyadoo la raacayo tilmaamaha ugu dambeeyay ee baaritaanka iyo daaweynta COVID-19 (daabacaadda toddobaad) iyo daraasado cusub.
Sida ku cad daabacaadda toddobaad (March 3, 2020), si loo caddeeyo kiis shaki leh waxaa loo baahan yahay in la isku daro mid ka mid ah astaamaha taariikhda cudurka faafa oo leh laba astaamood oo muujinaya calaamadaha si loo sameeyo falanqayn ballaaran, ama baahida loo qabo in la buuxiyo saddexda calaamadood haddii taariikhda cudurka faafa aysan caddaanin:
Taariikhda cudurka: (1) taariikhda safarka ama joogitaanka Wuhan iyo agagaarkeeda ama bulsho kale oo kiisaska COVID-19 laga soo sheegay 14kii maalmood ee ugu dambeeyay ka hor calaamadaha; (2) taariikhda xiriirka la leh SARS-CoV-2 (oo leh baaritaan wanaagsan oo ku saabsan nucleic acid); (3) taariikhda xiriirka bukaanka qandho leh ama qaba cudurrada neefsashada ee ka yimid Wuhan iyo agagaarka ama bulsho kale oo leh warbixin COVID-19 ah 14kii maalmood ee ugu dambeeyay ka hor calaamadaha; (4) taariikhda xiriirka sanka ee cudurka (≥ 2 kiis oo kulul / xanuun ama cudur la mid ah oo ku dhacay 2 toddobaad gudahood, ama ka dhacay aagga neefsashada, iwm.)
Calaamadaha caafimaad ee soo ifbaxa: (1) qandho iyo/ama calaamadaha neefsashada; (2) leh muuqaal muujinaya cudurka COVID-19; (3) tirada unugyada dhiigga oo guud ahaan muujinaya hoos u dhac caadi ah ama hoos u dhac tirada lymphatics ee marxaladda bilowga ah.
Cudurada cudurka waxaa lagu ogaan karaa marka la eego kiisaska laga shakiyo, ama haddii ay jiraan waxyeelooyin ama caddayn ah: (1) baaritaanka PCR ee waqtiga wanaagsan ee SARS-CoV-2 (2) taxanaha guud ee fayraska ayaa muujinaya isku midnimada sare ee loo yaqaan 'coronavirus', (3) baaritaanka serum ee antigen-ka 'IgM antigen' iyo antigen-ka 'IgG antigen' ee loo yaqaan 'SARS-CoV-2' ama isbeddelka antigen-ka 'IgG antigen' ee 'SARS-CoV-2' ee laga bilaabo mid taban ama mid togan ama ka badan 4 jeer ka badan heerka sare ee soo kabashada ee heerka hore ee baaritaanka.
Waxaan arki karnaa in baaritaanka falcelinta polymerase chain reaction ee nucleic acid ee baaritaanka wareegga dhiigga ama dhiigga lagu daray daabacaadda labaad (Janaayo 18, 2020) iyo saddexaad (Janaayo 22, 2020).
Caddeynta cudurka ee tijaabada dhiigga ayaa lagu daray daabacaadda afraad (Janaayo 27, 2020) iyo shanaad (Febraayo 8, 2020), ka dibna caddaynta baaritaanka dhiigga ayaa lagu daray daabacaadda toddobaad.
