ACE2 waa enzyme ku jira dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada, xididdada dhiigga, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo caloosha.
ACE2 waxay ka hortagtaa waxqabadka enzyme-ka loo yaqaan 'Acetyl-CoA-enzyme' (ACE) oo la xiriira hoos u dhigista tirada enzyme-II iyo kor u qaadista Angiotensin-II, taas oo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed daawo oo guul leh daaweynta cudurka wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa sida barta gelitaanka unugyada ee qaar ka mid ah fayrasyada corona.
Qeybta kale ee enzyme-ka ee bini'aadamka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Enzyme-de-termination-enzyme 2 waa xariiq bir ah oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada unugyada iyo unugyada kale.
ACE2 waxaa lagu xiraa N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo acid transporter domain oo leh qaab-dhismeedka C-terminal colectin.
ACE2 waa habka nooca I ee loo yaqaan 'protein binding pathway' oo ay enzymes-ka si toos ah ugu dhaqmaan dusha unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Dhinaca kale, ACE2 waxaa laga soo saaraa dhinaca kale ee loo yaqaan 'sedase' oo ah enzyme kale, halka borotiinka soo baxa uu ku sii daayo dhiigga, ugu dambeynna uu ku sii daayo sanka.
ACE2 waxay ku jirtaa inta badan unugyada: ACE2 waxay ku xirantahay unugyada unugyada nooca II ee sanbabada, unugyada xiidmaha yaryar, unugyada xididdada dhiigga iyo unugyada unugyada unugyada iyo unugyada muruqyada wareega ee unugyada unugyada badankood.
ACE2 mRNA waxaa sidoo kale laga helaa xayawaanka maskaxda ee maskaxda, hypothalamus iyo unugyada maskaxda.
Shaqada ugu weyn ee ACE2 waa inay noqoto mid isku dheelitiraya dheelitirka ACE.
ACE waxay u gudubtaa hormoonka 'antioxidant I' ee isku dhafka dhiigga ee 'antioxidant II'.
ACE2 waxay kala saartaa amino acid-ka karboksiil-terminal ee angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) waxayna u kala saartaa angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale dili kartaa qaar ka mid ah peptides kale oo ay ka mid yihiin [des-Arg9] - bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay ka caawisaa in la yareeyo heerarka gudbinta ee SLC6A19 iyo C ee loo yaqaan 'amino acid transporters' ee lagu arko cudurka Hartnup.
Sababtoo ah borotiinka ACE2 wuxuu u shaqeeyaa sida gelitaanka ugu muhiimsan ee unugyada qaar ka mid ah fayrasyada faafa, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus-ka sababa SARS) iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus-ka sababa COVID-19).
Si ka sii cad, isbeddelka borotiinka S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee loo yaqaan 'ACE2 enzymes' ee ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada, taas oo ka dhalatay kala-soocidda iyo baabi'inta goobta fayraska iyo enzymes-ka ee ku yaal unugyada.
Nidaamkan soo gelitaanka ayaa sidoo kale u baahan in borotiinka S uu ku jiro xayawaanka TMPRSS2 ee is-xidhka, joojinta ayaa la baaray inay tahay daaweyn suurtagal ah. Hawshani waxay keentay in qaar ay u maleynayaan in hoos u dhigista heerarka ACE2 ee unugyada ay ka caawin karto la dagaalanka infekshanka.
