Saldhigga ayaa ah xubinta ugu daran ee ay saameyso COVID-19 maadaama fayraska uu ku soo galo unugyada xambaara ee ku jira unugyada antibodies ee loo yaqaan 'antioxidant-converting enzyme 2' (ACE2), oo ay ku kala baxaan unugyada neefsashada ee yaryar ee nooca labaad ee sanbabada.
